data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.100 set value "The sun bakes everything here. Crops, spirits, the will to trade."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.101 set value "Saw a Patron out past the acacias last night. Glowing gray. Didn't sleep after."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.102 set value "Dust in my boots, dust in my lungs, dust in my future."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.103 set value "The wandering trader passed through. Sold me false hope and a lead."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.104 set value "A Furia tore through the eastern herd. Nothing Minor about it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.105 set value "I can see for miles out here. Mostly I see nothing worth seeing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.106 set value "Someone found a Heartstone in the old ruins. Kept it. Vanished a week later."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.107 set value "Pillagers came at dawn. We lost two fences and all our morale."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.108 set value "The llamas stare at me like they know something I don't."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.109 set value "Check your Codex before wandering south. That land doesn't forgive."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.110 set value "Rain? I think my grandfather mentioned it once."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.111 set value "An Expeditionist came through last season. Said our crates were picked clean."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.112 set value "Acacia wood doesn't burn clean, but it burns. That's enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.113 set value "The sky went violet two nights ago. Dream Surge, they called it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.114 set value "Flat land means you see the raids coming. Doesn't mean you can stop them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.115 set value "My neighbor swears he saw Mjolnir spark on the horizon. I believe him."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.116 set value "Every sunset here is worth dying for. Which is convenient."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.117 set value "The Guidestone hums louder when the wind picks up. Makes me uneasy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.118 set value "We don't have walls. We have stubbornness and a tired golem."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.119 set value "Someone left a mob head on the well post. Nobody claimed it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.120 set value "The dry grass hides bones. Old ones. From battles nobody recorded."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.121 set value "Heard the Artificer in the next village can fix anything. Except drought."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.122 set value "Horses on the ridge at sunset. Almost pretty enough to forget the hunger."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.123 set value "A Rare Patron wandered through the village square. Aqua glow, cold eyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.124 set value "I planted seeds in cracked dirt. Called it optimism."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.125 set value "The Structure Crate near the old tower refreshed. Everyone fought over it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.126 set value "Rabbits eat better than we do out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.127 set value "My companion wolf won't stop howling at the dry moon. Same, honestly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.128 set value "You want shade? Climb an acacia. That's the only shade we've got."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.129 set value "The Stormcaller artifact is just a rumor. A very loud rumor."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.130 set value "Another raid horn at dusk. We're running out of doors to barricade."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.131 set value "I checked my Advantage Tree. Spent everything on not dying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.132 set value "The heat makes the air shimmer. Or maybe that's a Greater Furia."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.133 set value "We used to have six villagers. Now there are four. Don't ask."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.134 set value "Found a Pebble of Dreams in the riverbed. Thought it was gravel at first."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.135 set value "The golem patrols the same dusty path. Day after day. I relate."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.136 set value "Illager scouts were spotted near the eastern ridge. Again."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.137 set value "A Hunter passed through and cleared out the skeleton problem. For now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.138 set value "The well's half sand. The bucket's half hope. Neither is enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.139 set value "Dream Rate's been high lately. Nightmares blooming like dry-season fires."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.140 set value "Creepers blend into the dry grass. Found that out the hard way."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.141 set value "They say Windrunner boots let you outrun anything. I'd settle for outrunning pillagers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.142 set value "This village has survived fourteen raids. We stopped celebrating after five."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.143 set value "The Tomb near the old battlefield still glows at night. We avoid it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.144 set value "I traded my last emerald for wheat. Worth it. Barely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.145 set value "An Ornate Patron came through at midnight. Purple glow. Beautiful and terrible."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.146 set value "The acacia trees bend but never break. We try to do the same."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.147 set value "Heard the Beekeeper two villages over has honey. Must be nice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.148 set value "Nowhere to hide on flat land. Just you and whatever's chasing you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.149 set value "Someone harmonized at the Guidestone and just... disappeared. Came back smiling."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.150 set value "The dust gets in everything. Food, beds, conversations."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.151 set value "A Miner told me there's diamonds under the savanna. I told him there's grief."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.152 set value "My chickens died. The heat or the skeletons. Does it matter?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.153 set value "The Ruin Watch ticks different out here. Like even time is tired."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.154 set value "I saw a ravager once. Only once. That was plenty."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.155 set value "The Earthshaker artifact supposedly splits the ground open. Savanna's already cracked."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.156 set value "We cook what the land gives us. Lately that's been dust soup."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.157 set value "Weapon Mastery sounds nice. I've mastered running away."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.158 set value "Endermen visit at night. They take blocks. We've stopped caring which ones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.159 set value "The Bartender in the mesa says life is harder there. I doubt it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.160 set value "Our iron golem got struck by lightning. Now it just stands and smokes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.161 set value "An Exquisite Patron was seen near the river. Pink glow. The fish all fled."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.162 set value "Sunsets paint the whole sky amber. Almost makes the suffering scenic."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.163 set value "My father farmed this land. His father too. The land still doesn't care."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.164 set value "The Nymph profession sounds peaceful. We don't get peaceful here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.165 set value "Someone dropped a Blaze Core near the well. Scorched the last good water."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.166 set value "Llama spit. That's the savanna welcome. Take it or leave."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.167 set value "The Wise Wanderer passed through but didn't stop. Even wisdom avoids us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.168 set value "I keep planting. The drought keeps winning. We're both committed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.169 set value "A Standard Furia chased the trader's llamas into the canyon. No survivors."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.170 set value "We sleep with one eye open. The other eye's too tired to bother."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.171 set value "Dragon Boots would be wasted here. Nowhere to fly but into more dust."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.172 set value "The bell rings for raids. It rang three times this week."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.173 set value "I saw a mob head collection once. Disturbing. Also impressive."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.174 set value "The horizon shimmers in the heat. Could be a mirage. Could be a Furia."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.175 set value "An Uncommon Patron stalked the treeline. Blue glow. The livestock panicked."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.176 set value "Every acacia tree is a monument to stubbornness. I respect that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.177 set value "A Retired Adventurer settled here. Lasted two seasons. Went back to adventuring."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.178 set value "The stars are clear at least. Hard to complain about the sky."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.179 set value "The Acacia Ballista is just a legend. Right? Please say right."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.180 set value "Water's so scarce the cows look at me with judgment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.181 set value "Someone used a Guidestone to leave. Can't blame them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.182 set value "Spiders come at night. We've named the regulars."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.183 set value "The Zookeeper profession would be funny here. Our zoo is two chickens."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.184 set value "Pillager crossbows crack louder on flat land. The sound carries for miles."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.185 set value "I dream of green biomes. Then I wake up to brown."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.186 set value "A Mythical Patron. Gold glow. I heard the ground shook for an hour."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.187 set value "We measure good days by how little went wrong."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.188 set value "The old Structure Crate at the ruins has been empty for weeks now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.189 set value "My bed is acacia planks and dried grass. It's honest, at least."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.190 set value "Saw someone checking their Codex in the shade. Shade hog."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.191 set value "The evokers are the worst. At least skeletons are straightforward about killing you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.192 set value "A pet cat wandered in from the plains. Thinks it's too good for us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.193 set value "If I had a companion parrot, at least someone would talk to me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.194 set value "Twilight here lasts forever. Orange sky bleeding into purple. Worth the misery."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.195 set value "The Dream Surge made the phantoms worse. Violet sky, violet nightmares."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.196 set value "Another traveler with enchanted gear passing through. Must be nice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.197 set value "We had a witch attack last full moon. My potatoes never recovered."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.198 set value "The Uncommon crate loot was just string. String. In the savanna."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.199 set value "I heard the Expeditionist profession reduces crate cooldowns. Wish I could do that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.200 set value "Hot wind, dry earth, and the distant sound of something growling. Morning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.201 set value "The village elder says hardship builds character. We have too much character."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.202 set value "A traveler tried to Harmonize at our Guidestone. Nothing happened. Figures."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.203 set value "Even the zombies look dehydrated out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.204 set value "Heard about the Advantage Tree upgrades. We can't even upgrade our roof."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.205 set value "My composter is the most exciting thing in this village. Sad."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.206 set value "A Minor Furia circled the village at dawn. Even chaos gets up early here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.207 set value "The trader's llamas ate our last flowers. We're even now on disappointment."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.208 set value "Found an old artifact shard in the field. Turned out to be flint."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.209 set value "The flat expanse goes on forever. So does the loneliness."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.210 set value "Someone told me about the Tomb system. Dying with a backup plan. Novel."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.211 set value "I named my hoe. We've been through too much together not to."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.212 set value "A Common Patron with the gray cross. Barely glowing. Still killed two cows."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.213 set value "The horizon is a straight line. No hills, no trees, no mercy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.214 set value "Weapon Mastery won't help when your weapon is a wooden hoe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.215 set value "The acacia bark peels in the heat. Just like my skin."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.216 set value "Mob heads on fence posts. Someone's been decorating. Unsettling but effective."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.217 set value "Last Dream Surge brought strange creatures. Glowing things in the tall grass."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.218 set value "I envy the forest villagers. They have shade AND self-respect."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.219 set value "The well dried up. We drink stubbornness now."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.220 set value "An artifact hunter came through asking about the Stormcaller. Pointed them south."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.221 set value "We keep going. Not sure why. Habit, probably."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.222 set value "The cats here have given up on mice. There are no mice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.223 set value "A Greater Furia nearly leveled the outpost west of here. Just... gone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.224 set value "Phantoms overhead every third night. We've stopped flinching."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.225 set value "They say the Codex has entries for everything. Even our suffering? Doubt it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.226 set value "The night brings skeletons. The day brings heat. Pick your poison."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.227 set value "I heard a Patron named Ashveil roams these flats. Hope that's just gossip."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.228 set value "My grandfather planted these acacias. The drought tried to kill them. Failed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.229 set value "The Rare crate tier had an artifact chance. We got leather boots."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.230 set value "Savanna mornings smell like dry grass and quiet desperation."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.231 set value "I tried taming a horse once. It ran toward the pillager outpost. Smart horse."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.232 set value "Every emerald I earn goes back into not starving. Good system."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.233 set value "The wandering trader charged me double. For dead bushes. Dead. Bushes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.234 set value "If the Dream Rate keeps climbing, even the golem will start having nightmares."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.235 set value "We had a celebration once. Then a creeper joined. Short celebration."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.236 set value "The crate loot refreshes eventually. My patience doesn't."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.237 set value "I watch the sunset because it's free and it doesn't try to kill me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.238 set value "Heard the Acacia Ballista fires thorns. Sounds like something we'd invent here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.239 set value "My neighbor keeps talking about a companion he wants. A wolf. Out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.240 set value "Savanna nights are cold. Nobody warns you about the cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.241 set value "An Ornate crate dropped something purple once. Elder took it. Won't say what."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.242 set value "The golem killed a skeleton today. We threw a small party. Very small."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.243 set value "I look at the Guidestone and wonder where everyone went."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.244 set value "Vindicators hit harder than you'd expect. Trust me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.245 set value "A traveler left a Ruin Watch behind. Ticking. Nobody touches it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.246 set value "Llamas, dust, and acacias. That's the whole sales pitch for this biome."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.247 set value "The Exquisite tier crate is just a myth around here. We get Common."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.248 set value "I sleep on a bed I built from fallen branches. Luxury."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.249 set value "A Furia with the star mark circled overhead. We just watched."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.250 set value "Sometimes the wind dies and everything goes silent. That's worse."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.251 set value "The Patron system terrifies me. Named elites that hunt you. Beautiful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.252 set value "I saw a player use Dragon Boots to fly over our village. Didn't stop."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.253 set value "My crops are brown. My mood is brown. The sky, at least, is orange."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.254 set value "The Tomb marker near the canyon means someone died there. Permanently, I hope not."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.255 set value "We don't fear the dark. We fear what glows in it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.256 set value "The Pebble of Dreams sounds small. Small things survive out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.257 set value "Spiders the size of dogs. Endermen taller than the huts. Normal Tuesday."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.258 set value "A Bartender? Out here? We'd drink cactus juice and call it fine dining."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.259 set value "The ridge holds old ruins. Nobody goes there after the last Furia sighting."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.260 set value "I heard the Dream Surge changes what spawns at night. We noticed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.261 set value "My only luxury is watching the llamas argue with each other."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.262 set value "Pillager outpost on the horizon. Been there longer than our village."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.263 set value "Weapon Mastery takes practice. I've mastered the art of enduring."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.264 set value "The Mythical gold glow is supposed to be beautiful. I never want to see it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.265 set value "A companion wolf would be nice. Something warm that doesn't judge."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.266 set value "I tell the children stories about green biomes. They think I'm lying."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.267 set value "The Structure Crate timer feels longer every time. Or maybe that's just me."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.268 set value "Acacia country. Where the trees grow crooked and so do the people."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.269 set value "I respect anyone who chose Expeditionist. They walk toward the things I run from."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.270 set value "The dry grass catches fire if you look at it wrong. Blaze Core territory."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.271 set value "Night here sounds like bone rattles and distant moaning. You get used to it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.272 set value "I've been told the Codex tracks everything. Even my losses, I imagine."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.273 set value "A donkey stood outside my hut for three days. Neither of us moved."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.274 set value "The Dream Surge violet is actually quite lovely. Shame about the monsters."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.275 set value "Our strongest fence post was an acacia log and a prayer."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.276 set value "Heard a Patron has a name that shows above its head. Personalized terror."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.277 set value "Sometimes a breeze comes through and we all just stand in it. Silently."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.278 set value "The Earthshaker would be redundant here. The ground already shakes from raids."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.279 set value "If you've got a Guidestone destination, take me with you. Please."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.280 set value "The savanna sunset lasts an hour. Best hour of every terrible day."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.281 set value "Someone asked me about mob heads. I pointed at the pile behind the hut."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.282 set value "A Rare Patron with the aqua shimmer. Named itself after our village. Rude."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.283 set value "The heat and the cold take turns making us miserable. Efficient."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.284 set value "I dug a hole once. Just to have something to do. Filled it back in."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.285 set value "You ever see the Advantage Tree fully unlocked? Me neither. Just dreaming."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.286 set value "The Harmonize glow at the Guidestone is the prettiest thing in this biome."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.287 set value "We lost a cow to a skeleton. Not a creeper, not a raid. A skeleton. Sad."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.288 set value "My grandmother survived forty raids. Set the bar impossibly high."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.289 set value "A Furia doesn't care about your walls. Or your feelings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.290 set value "The Wandering Trader sells tropical fish here. The audacity."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.291 set value "I planted a sapling. It grew into more acacia. Of course it did."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.292 set value "The old battlefield under the eastern grass still has armor scraps."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.293 set value "Someone claimed an artifact dropped from an Exquisite crate here. Liars thrive everywhere."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.294 set value "Dusk is when the endermen come. And the memories."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.295 set value "The Wise Wanderer profession fits this place. Lots of wandering. Little wisdom."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.296 set value "My hut leans east now. The wind's been winning that argument for years."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.297 set value "I once saw a Stormcaller strike bring rain. One minute of rain. Wept."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.298 set value "Savanna resilience is just despair that learned to walk upright."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.299 set value "The stars are the same ones the plains folk see. Ours just look lonelier."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.300 set value "Build us walls. Thick ones. Please."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.301 set value "The old settlement east of here had stone walls. Now it's rubble and weeds."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.302 set value "Could you build a watchtower? We need eyes above the grass line."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.303 set value "There's a battlefield under the southern field. Nobody farms there anymore."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.304 set value "A deep well would change everything. Even just one that holds water."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.305 set value "They say a fortress stood here before the pillagers. All that's left is foundation stones."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.306 set value "Build us a gathering hall. We need somewhere to be miserable together."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.307 set value "The barren ridge was a trading route once. Before the Furia came."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.308 set value "A roof that doesn't leak dust. That's all I'm asking for."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.309 set value "Three villages used to dot these flats. We're the only one left."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.310 set value "Build a livestock pen with a gate that actually closes. Revolutionary idea."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.311 set value "The canyon carved itself deeper every season. Something old runs underneath."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.312 set value "Lanterns on the paths would help. We lose people to ravines at night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.313 set value "The old settlers carved warnings into the acacia stumps. We can't read them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.314 set value "A proper irrigation channel. Water from the river to the fields. Simple but vital."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.315 set value "Bones surface after every hard wind. This land remembers what we don't."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.316 set value "Build a stable. Not for horses we have. For horses we might find."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.317 set value "The ruins on the plateau held a community once. Bigger than ours."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.318 set value "A shaded market stall. Even a bad trade feels better out of the sun."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.319 set value "The dry river was a trade lifeline two generations ago. Now it's a scar."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.320 set value "Reinforce the bell post. Last raid knocked it over. Couldn't warn anyone."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.321 set value "Something ancient burned this savanna flat. The soil still tastes like ash."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.322 set value "Build me a cellar. Cool storage underground. The heat spoils everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.323 set value "Iron swords in the dirt near the eastern ridge. Nobody claims that history."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.324 set value "A firebreak around the village. Dry grass and lightning are old enemies."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.325 set value "The standing stones on the hilltop predate our village by centuries."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.326 set value "Build a rain collector. When it finally comes, we'll be ready."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.327 set value "Old arrow shafts in the western field. Hundreds. A battle we never knew."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.328 set value "A proper smithy with an anvil. Our tools break faster than our spirits."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.329 set value "The savanna erases everything eventually. Roads, walls, names. We build anyway."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.330 set value "Could use a covered bridge over the ravine. Lost a cow down there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.331 set value "Charred stone pillars in the field. No one knows what they held up."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.332 set value "A lookout post with a horn. Early warning is all we have."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.333 set value "The old mines are sealed. Something collapsed them. Or someone sealed them shut."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.334 set value "Build a monument. Something that says we were here and we held on."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.335 set value "Carved stone under the acacia roots. Writing from people who came before."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.336 set value "A windbreak wall on the north side. The cold wind cuts right through us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.337 set value "The flat stones near the creek are too even to be natural. Old foundations."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.338 set value "Fix the path to the Guidestone. Shouldn't have to risk a broken ankle to teleport."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.339 set value "The savanna was green once. The elders swear it. I want to believe them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.340 set value "Build a beacon fire on the hill. Let travelers know someone's still alive here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.341 set value "Pottery shards in the riverbed. A whole civilization washed downstream."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.342 set value "An archway at the village entrance. Something that says welcome and means it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.343 set value "The battle cairn on the ridge has fresh flowers sometimes. Nobody admits to placing them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.344 set value "A bench under the bent acacia. Somewhere to sit and watch the nothing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.345 set value "The old watchtower base still stands. Just needs rebuilding. Like everything here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.346 set value "A storage shed that locks. The endermen take things. The villagers also take things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.347 set value "Weapon racks on the wall. Even decorative ones make the pillagers think twice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.348 set value "Skull fragments in the dry creek bed. This savanna has seen worse than us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.savanna.349 set value "Build something that lasts. Out here, that alone would be a miracle."
